crop.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><small>Outside Da Lat Market at night</small></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ã„ï¿½&agrave; LÃ¡ÂºÂ¡t\'s specific sights are pine wood (forming the name: \"City of thousands of pine trees\") with twisting roads and tree marigold (Vietnamese: d&atilde; quÃ¡Â»Â³) blossom in the winter. The city\'s temperate weather stands in contrast to Vietnam\'s otherwise tropical climate. Mist covering the valleys almost year-round leads to its name \"City of eternal spring.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde738539_crop.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Da Lat\'s Market square at night</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ã„ï¿½&agrave; LÃ¡ÂºÂ¡t is also known as an area for science research in the fields of biotechnology and nuclear physics.<br /><br />With its year-round cool weather, Ã„ï¿½&agrave; LÃ¡ÂºÂ¡t supplies temperate agriculture products for all over Vietnam, for example, cabbage and cauliflower. Its flower industry produces two typical flowers: hydrangea (Vietnamese: cÃ¡ÂºÂ©m t&uacute; cÃ¡ÂºÂ§u) and golden everlasting (Vietnamese: hoa bÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t tÃ¡Â»Â­). The confectionery industry offers a wide range of mÃ¡Â»Â©t, a kind of fruit preserve made from strawberry, mulberry, sweet potato, and rose.</p>','Wikipedia','','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_square.jpeg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_thumbnail.jpeg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_small.jpeg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_crop.jpeg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_medium.jpeg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbd8c1bde4_large.jpeg','active',3,'2010-08-31 15:30:10',1,'admin','2010-08-31 15:43:17',1,'admin',1,'admin','2010-08-31 15:30:17',0,0,0,0,NULL,0,'en_US'),(