ll bowl of soup broth (canh) with garlic chives (to cleanse the throat).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce1fb72ae2_crop.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>CÃ†Â¡m tÃ¡ÂºÂ¥m with grilled pork, shredded pork, pork skin, fried egg, pork meatloaf, pickled carrot, and sliced cucumber</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Broken_Rice\" class=\"mw-headline\">Broken Rice</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Some rice grains break in the transport and processing of the rice from the field to the pot. Machinery is available to separate the broken grains from the whole grains. Broken rice may or may not have lower fiber and nutrient content, but generally has a similar energy content to intact rice.<br /><br />The broken varieties are often less expensive, so are preferred by poorer consumers or used as raw material (such as in beer brewing). ue to the different size and shape of the grains, broken rice has a different texture from \"unbroken\" rice. Some chefs and consumers may prefer the qualities of broken rice for certain dishes.</p>','Wikipedia','','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_square.jpg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_thumbnail.jpg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_small.jpg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_crop.jpg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_medium.jpg','/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce2687f4e4_large.jpg','active',1,'2010-08-31 18:07:28',1,'admin',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'admin','2010-08-31 18:07:36',0,0,0,0,NULL,0,'en_US'),(42,19,'CÃ†Â¡m tÃ¡ÂºÂ¥m','','com-tam','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CÃ†Â¡m tÃ¡ÂºÂ¥m l&agrave; m&oacute;n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ·c sÃ¡ÂºÂ£n cÃ¡Â»Â§a miÃ¡Â»ï¿½n Nam ViÃ¡Â»â€¡t Nam, n&oacute; l&agrave; mÃ¡Â»â„¢t trong nhÃ¡Â»Â¯ng m&oacute;n Ã„Æ’n s&aacute;ng Ã„â€˜Ã†Â°Ã¡Â»Â£c Ã†Â°a chuÃ¡Â»â„¢ng nhÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t cÃ¡Â»Â§a ngÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½i miÃ¡Â»ï¿½n Nam